job.title: MPPGCL Apprentice Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 209 Vacancies in Bangalore
job.body:
Total vacancies:400

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Graduate Apprentice & Technician 

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for Diploma/B.Tech has been published by Bangalore Electricity Supply Company Limited for Graduate Apprentice & Technician vacancies in Bangalore. If you are searching for a government job in Bangalore then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Graduate Apprentice & Technician, from 14-07-2021, and till 16-08-2021. If you are interested in all these vacancies in Bangalore and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • no information about the application fee

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Graduate Apprentice & Technician in MPPGCL, your Graduation must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 16-08-2021 till 11:59 PM

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 21 to 35 years old. 

MPPGCL Graduate Apprentice & Technician Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for MPPGCL Apprentice Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Technician. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of MPPGCL and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by MPPGCL
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
